    "Kobayashi et al. (2007) first utilizes dependency trees to find candidate aspect and opinion word pairs and then employs tree structure classification methods to learn and categorize these word pairs.",
    "Aspect extraction is a specific case of information extraction.",
    "Therefore, sequence learning models such as Hidden Markov Models (HMM) and Conditional Random Fields (CRF) can be used for aspect extraction.",
